public class LoggerRunnable implements Runnable {

    public LoggerRunnable() {
        Thread thread = new Thread(this); // this escapes
        thread.start();
    }

    @Override
    public void run() {
        System.out.println("Started...");
    }
}
```

```
public class ImplicitEscape {

    public ImplicitEscape() {
        Thread t = new Thread() {

            @Override
            public void run() {
                System.out.println("Started...");
            }
        };

        t.start();
    }
}
```

